{"tid":2275358,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲: We can check claims but we can't check facts.","createTime":"2020-11-07T05:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T10:30:39.000Z","uid":78016,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0943e138dfda0ddd6371bcfb3be65ce521cecf3a","tid":2275358,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:55:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157392200197225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157392200197225&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuIXq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=2de509e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157392200197225</a><br />\n<br />\n轉載自陳雲 fb<br />\n大家對fact check 嘅爭拗 可以睇返呢位痴線佬嘅分析 再諗下自己係咪痴線食左藥未<br />\n留言之前我真心建議你睇一睇呢位痴線佬對fact check 嘅見解<br />\n你遇到5毛笑鳩你fact check 你都識反駁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1096a02b86432dde0009c925ca9ccbd60f794ca9","tid":2275358,"uid":78016,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"&quot;事實好像是無可懷疑的。但事實是法相（佛陀的詞）、是物自身（德國哲學家康德的詞），是觀念認為可以建構事實的各種考驗通過了之後的建構物，邏輯上是弔詭的。故此我們可以說查證某個宣稱，但我們不能查證事實。(We can check claims but we can't check facts. And all facts are claimed facts.) 當大家聲稱要查證事實的時候，事實的公認性就消失&quot;"},{"pid":"7a408acb09b19afe2a786ed23e95218d4b796887","tid":2275358,"uid":126782,"like":11,"dislike":12,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"麻煩陳雲嘅野唔好拎上連登<br />\n<br />\n拎返去匡智會"},{"pid":"2c895c7db86c53979a4d2d12e7acc0f5d829ffca","tid":2275358,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"你係五毛pr熱狗，fact check左"},{"pid":"de825aaa0d1bb7c2c9bbb5141cdea96391dd03b5","tid":2275358,"uid":271397,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"雲根一貫嘅文字遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢